title: Episode 168: Russell Hartley - Real Life Hitch
description:
Show Notes:

In this episode I interview Russell Hartley, who I met through TikTok who is an author, social media personality, and dating coach. The infamous "ex-player," Russell has reached millions of people by recounting his unique (and controversial) stories about his dating experiences in Los Angeles. His signature look includes wearing bespoke suits and luxury brands that catch the attention of his viewers who appreciate his classic style.
